Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.05,0:00:52.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何都要去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.63,0:00:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约定好的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.22,0:01:00.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“一定会去见他”
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.81,0:01:05.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去的话可就再也回不来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.27,0:01:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.82,0:01:17.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别走 求求你别走！ 我...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.86,0:01:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对你...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.87,0:01:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,6...5...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.86,0:01:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4...3...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.01,0:01:25.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.22,0:01:26.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.17,0:01:26.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,0
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.27,0:01:53.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.98,0:01:56.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社长 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.32,0:01:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,器材呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.20,0:01:59.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 车也准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.03,0:02:01.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这就来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.07,0:04:06.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近 银映股份公司
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.62,0:04:12.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被迫决定关闭设施陈旧的原摄影棚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.33,0:04:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为纪念 这次企划
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.58,0:04:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将对支撑银映创立70年历史的大明星
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.17,0:04:24.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤原千代子小姐的足迹进行追随...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.89,0:04:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽拍我干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.76,0:04:31.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能再早些来这取材就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.85,0:04:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,区区一次采访早点答应又怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.11,0:04:39.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人已经不是影艺圈人士了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.94,0:04:45.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真要取材的话应该30年前去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.91,0:04:54.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隐居在这么难走的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.96,0:04:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个古怪的老太婆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.00,0:05:00.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再说看我不宰了你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.42,0:05:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过社长 再厉害的女演员
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.51,0:05:09.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过了70的话 那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.56,0:05:11.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不都会变成老态龙钟吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.64,0:05:14.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.56,0:05:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那里！就是那里！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.06,0:05:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是不要抱什么幻想为好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.40,0:05:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道现在是什么模样...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.36,0:05:26.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人不会上年纪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.83,0:05:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.00,0:05:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.30,0:05:52.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤原小姐一个人住这房子？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.77,0:05:55.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 一直这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.64,0:06:00.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消遣的话也就是看看书和在园子里摆弄摆弄花草
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.19,0:06:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这香茶也是夫人亲手做的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.32,0:06:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们运气真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.08,0:06:14.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到夫人她会同意接受采访
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.16,0:06:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当初因为连地址也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.00,0:06:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到这里吃了不少苦头
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.62,0:06:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们真的感到非常荣幸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.58,0:06:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是有特别的礼物带绐夫人？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.71,0:06:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊...是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.97,0:06:29.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪不得呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.76,0:06:33.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夫人会乐于见人真是大事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.26,0:06:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出了什么大事？美浓阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.56,0:06:37.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.85,0:06:39.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是异变
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.27,0:06:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,异·变
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.23,0:06:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在说今晨的地震
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.61,0:06:44.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时吓了我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.53,0:06:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真以为是大限到了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.53,0:06:53.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面 我是藤原千代子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.62,0:06:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今日如此风和日丽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.91,0:06:59.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...我等能来此造访也甚感荣幸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.62,0:07:01.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么拘谨可不好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.34,0:07:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制片厂...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.00,0:07:06.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,读作LOTUS
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.59,0:07:08.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是睡莲的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.01,0:07:11.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.84,0:07:16.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是知道这点所以把社名也...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.68,0:07:20.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就要开了 屋后园子里的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.10,0:07:23.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花语 知道吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.94,0:07:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记得应该是“纯真”
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.70,0:07:34.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来立花先生 那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.74,0:07:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是我一时疏忽...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.54,0:07:45.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本想寄来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.75,0:07:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不清楚这里的通讯地址
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.42,0:07:51.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以亲自带来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.93,0:08:00.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本以为已经忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.85,0:08:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问 是很重要的东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.23,0:08:08.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打开最珍贵东西的钥匙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.82,0:08:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 立花先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.03,0:08:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你是怎么得到这把钥匙的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.91,0:08:19.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个...这个嘛...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.45,0:08:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前有人在银映的摄影棚里拾到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.46,0:08:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从没想过能再次拿到它
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.77,0:08:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.11,0:08:49.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连地震都在为我们祝贺了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.78,0:08:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.32,0:08:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和地震也许真的很有缘份
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.45,0:09:01.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 我出生都是和地震一起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.58,0:09:07.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关东大地震
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.38,0:09:11.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期盼着接班人的家父
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.55,0:09:14.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这次地震中去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.84,0:09:17.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直就象是作为交换我来到这世上一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.26,0:09:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.56,0:09:22.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠着父亲遗留下的店铺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.31,0:09:27.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和母亲二人的生活还算温饱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.65,0:09:34.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的孩童时代
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.78,0:09:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整个世界就象赌博一样危机重重
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.78,0:09:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么东西都一个劲住右拐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.70,0:09:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（万岁、万岁、万岁）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.09,0:09:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.34,0:09:58.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时的我更看重的是少女杂志
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.34,0:10:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到插画就幻想着和白马王子的邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.77,0:10:08.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被银映相中就是那时候的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.27,0:10:13.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不知道塌鼻梁的我到底哪里好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.65,0:10:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是银映的常务董事看中了在上女校的我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.67,0:10:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何都不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.92,0:10:32.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.09,0:10:35.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位是常务董事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.55,0:10:40.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我母亲说女演员不正派反对我去做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.84,0:10:43.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不正派...吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.60,0:10:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.06,0:10:48.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次以满洲为舞台的新作品
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.44,0:10:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够鼓舞为国奋战的士兵们和所有日本国民
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.82,0:10:58.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千代子君也一定想为国家出份力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.90,0:10:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.91,0:11:03.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话虽这么说董事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.45,0:11:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样怕羞的孩子怎么看也不是做演员的料
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.66,0:11:10.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她必须给我找个女婿继承家业
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.37,0:11:12.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.50,0:11:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国家和糖果店哪个重要！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.80,0:11:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非要说是为了国家的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.42,0:11:21.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人保护家庭生儿育女也是本分
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.26,0:11:22.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.98,0:12:15.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.77,0:12:18.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么采访？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.28,0:12:25.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千代子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.70,0:12:27.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么感觉象尾随狂一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.21,0:12:34.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.00,0:12:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为急着赶路
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.26,0:12:49.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然有气氛了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.06,0:12:51.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社长别挡着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.31,0:12:57.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没见到！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.44,0:12:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绕到那边去！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.37,0:13:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩 见到有个男人经过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.08,0:13:19.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱着很大包裹皮的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.02,0:13:36.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往那跑去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.52,0:13:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.74,0:14:37.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庇护逃犯胆子还真不小啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.00,0:14:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那男人是谁！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.42,0:14:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能看看吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.84,0:14:46.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还刚开始画
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.34,0:14:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打算等回故乡后继续完成这画
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.47,0:14:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出生的城市
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.27,0:15:00.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了冬天就会被绵延到天边的白雪覆盖
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.40,0:15:02.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一望无际
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.94,0:15:05.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想在那里架起画架
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.03,0:15:07.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,边感受着刺骨的寒冷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.24,0:15:09.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,边完成这幅画
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.03,0:15:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦身处那广阔而雪白的风景中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.45,0:15:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会有种置身于遥远星球上般不可思议的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.13,0:15:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也好想去一次
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.88,0:15:30.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.34,0:15:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和平来到后
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.22,0:15:34.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为救我的回报
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.10,0:15:36.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时一定请你来作客
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.94,0:15:45.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,满月
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.44,0:15:48.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天才是满月
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.15,0:15:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我更喜欢这时候的月亮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.07,0:15:56.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,满月从下一天开始就会月缺
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.58,0:16:00.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而十四日的月亮却还有明天
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.79,0:16:03.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有被称为明天的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.63,0:16:07.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又要上路了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.59,0:16:09.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但伤势还...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.88,0:16:13.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伙伴们在满洲战斗着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.89,0:16:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠画具和笔恐怕难有作为
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.89,0:16:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.69,0:16:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是打开最珍贵东西的钥匙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.11,0:16:30.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最珍贵的东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.36,0:16:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猜猜看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.74,0:16:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猜不到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.28,0:16:38.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过先别告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.70,0:16:42.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当做明天的作业 约好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.17,0:16:54.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快老实交代
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.26,0:16:57.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有心上人了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.43,0:16:59.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初恋？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.18,0:17:03.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.44,0:17:12.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.03,0:17:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前的人当然不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.15,0:17:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社长带来的钥匙是...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.58,0:18:08.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该还在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.12,0:18:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔细找
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.13,0:18:09.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.89,0:18:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.85,0:18:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.18,0:18:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎有贼躲进我们家仓库里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.56,0:18:28.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安全逃脱了 快去车站
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.23,0:18:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您没受伤实在太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.57,0:18:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一套嘛 掌柜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.63,0:19:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是累死人的采访
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.34,0:19:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.88,0:19:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.14,0:19:45.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.48,0:19:57.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会去的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.61,0:20:00.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会去见你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.20,0:20:08.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好浪漫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.21,0:20:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在影院里为这场景哭了53次
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.55,0:20:20.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候开始说电影的事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.17,0:20:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.09,0:20:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此后就进入了电影的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.39,0:20:29.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.02,0:20:31.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后就踏入电影界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.40,0:20:35.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可以这样说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.61,0:20:38.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前董事不也说过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.19,0:20:42.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一部电影是以满洲为舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.49,0:20:45.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,满洲...对了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.49,0:20:48.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 千代子君
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.62,0:20:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道你一定会接受的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.58,0:20:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我也想为国家出力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.25,0:20:57.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.59,0:21:00.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.88,0:21:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了到满洲去追寻“键之君”
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.55,0:21:08.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电影什么的那时根本不在乎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.81,0:21:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千代子君
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.73,0:21:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是这次的主角
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.31,0:21:15.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤原千代子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.81,0:21:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.98,0:21:20.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位相信你也认识
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.44,0:21:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的招牌女璃员 岛尾咏子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.53,0:21:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多关照 藤原"千惠子"小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.76,0:21:47.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是悠闲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.60,0:21:49.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.85,0:21:52.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.43,0:21:54.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.52,0:21:56.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是叔父
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.06,0:21:58.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到个好演员
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.27,0:22:02.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少爷的手还真快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.90,0:22:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是叫藤原“千津子”吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.16,0:22:10.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是千代子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.87,0:22:11.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.29,0:22:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,董事的侄子大泷先生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.91,0:22:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是前途无量的导演大人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.25,0:22:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对女演员已经做过实地调查了？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.71,0:22:25.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的恶作剧不好意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.09,0:22:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是代人保管的重要东西
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.51,0:22:33.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果在满洲遇见那人很想交还给他
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.27,0:22:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不是去玩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.14,0:22:39.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁？那个键之君
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.56,0:22:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.44,0:22:44.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话不是根本没法找吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.32,0:22:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是画画的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.70,0:22:47.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么画？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.03,0:22:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.36,0:22:50.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也不知道吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.08,0:22:52.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.49,0:22:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他一定在这满洲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.66,0:23:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道呢 我可不认识这样的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.09,0:23:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.63,0:23:08.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但 的确听说是在这附近
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.30,0:23:11.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外行人在身边会碍手碍脚的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.72,0:23:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能因为你这样说就轻易放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.85,0:23:19.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易下定决心飘洋过海来到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.02,0:23:22.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...我...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.57,0:23:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么回事 导演！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.82,0:23:29.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她怎么连台词都没背好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.16,0:23:31.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先等等
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.99,0:23:36.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千代子君 台词这东西
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.87,0:23:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是完全进入角色后自然而然发自内心的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.75,0:23:42.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.42,0:23:43.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我说过了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.79,0:23:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是外行人随便能演的角色
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.76,0:23:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...无论如何想见那人一眼！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.97,0:23:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.10,0:23:57.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 开始正式拍摄
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.85,0:24:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.98,0:24:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 了不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.52,0:24:08.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很出色的演技
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.74,0:24:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？从刚才开始
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.82,0:24:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来怎么样了？键之君的线索
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.41,0:24:20.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到你还挺耿耿于怀的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.08,0:24:22.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正也没什幺目标的话
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.54,0:24:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如去算一卦如何
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.13,0:24:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那旁边的算卦先生
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.34,0:24:30.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说很准哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.01,0:24:40.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此人看来是在北面
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.27,0:24:44.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个画家 个子很高
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.56,0:24:47.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非那男人是在找寻一把钥匙？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.44,0:24:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您知道吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.32,0:24:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那男人应该在...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.74,0:25:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请告诉我 那人现在在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.34,0:25:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样把拍摄丢下不管了？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.76,0:25:17.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真是乱来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.97,0:25:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种一心一意的少女之心都不懂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.43,0:25:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想被社长这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.31,0:25:28.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北满洲大量日裔革命人士遭检举
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.77,0:25:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过社长
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.40,0:25:33.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被这么拼命的追赶
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.70,0:25:35.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也算是男人最大的幸福了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.78,0:25:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想被追追看
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.25,0:25:47.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千代子小姐！千代子小姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.38,0:25:49.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国民党吗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.75,0:25:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,共军吗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.38,0:25:52.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看！那边
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.51,0:25:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是马贼的袭击！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.22,0:26:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤原小姐 千代子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.18,0:26:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也太有现实感了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.85,0:26:07.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千代子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.77,0:26:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请振作些 千代子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.65,0:26:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.15,0:26:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社长快逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.98,0:26:54.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这哪里是马贼！
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.74,0:26:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是...发生什么事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.74,0:27:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还想问呢
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.41,0:27:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,满洲上哪去了 满洲
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.67,0:27:16.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.84,0:27:17.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.22,0:27:19.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殿下还在天守阁中
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.22,0:27:19.97,comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天守阁：日本城堡中心的了望楼
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.85,0:27:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万万不可 公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.08,0:27:45.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殿下！
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.70,0:27:46.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殿下！
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.33,0:27:53.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何不能等公主一步呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.00,0:27:57.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.67,0:27:59.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哭了几遍？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.36,0:28:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.62,0:28:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是传说中居于此城的妖魔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.42,0:28:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何称呼我都无妨
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.34,0:28:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在你出生前便对你的事了如指掌
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.68,0:28:50.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这妖魔现在前来有何贵干
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.73,0:28:54.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非还想送我一程？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.94,0:29:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝下这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.61,0:29:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今生无法结合之身
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.70,0:29:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在冥府魔道之地想必定能如愿
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.91,0:29:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要我抛弃人身？
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.25,0:29:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人已经等你很久了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.28,0:29:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此乃千年长命茶！
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.91,0:29:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从今往后你将受恋火焚身永世不得超度
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.58,0:29:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你设计了我
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.17,0:30:01.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我恨你 恨之入骨
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.76,0:30:07.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,且爱你 如痴如醉
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.26,0:30:11.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天你会明白！
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.66,0:30:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了 社长
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.34,0:30:49.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主！长门守源卫门前来护驾
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.30,0:30:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候换的
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.89,0:30:56.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下即使豁出性命也要救出公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.94,0:31:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主 不能离开殿下身边
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.95,0:31:10.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 妖魔
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.74,0:31:14.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无奈殿下己被敌人所擒
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.37,0:31:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殿下尚在人间？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.50,0:31:20.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下 请尽快赶回国
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.55,0:31:29.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前去救回殿下！
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.39,0:31:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟上！寅吉
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.27,0:31:42.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是谁啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.19,0:31:46.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.94,0:31:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,—定要到殿下身边
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.59,0:32:12.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.56,0:32:17.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长门！
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.10,0:32:19.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.56,0:32:23.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的忠心 决不忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.73,0:32:26.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝武运...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.07,0:32:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直就象昨天发生的事一样
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.95,0:32:38.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗 就这样下去
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.50,0:32:44.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能这样听藤原夫人的叙述是我们的光荣
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.59,0:32:46.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.38,0:32:51.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才说到哪了？
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.43,0:32:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突破敌人的包围...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.68,0:32:57.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“长门守战死之卷”
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.26,0:32:58.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.06,0:33:03.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何都想救出被抓的那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.93,0:33:36.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.05,0:33:37.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歹人！有歹人！
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.22,0:33:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笼子
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.31,0:33:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看好犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.98,0:33:44.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我 我来救您了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.65,0:33:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想抢先我一步
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.57,0:33:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还早十年呢
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.24,0:33:58.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才不还是公主吗
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.63,0:34:13.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千代子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.47,0:34:14.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背后！
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.93,0:34:21.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把她解决
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.47,0:34:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.69,0:34:26.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.11,0:34:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.24,0:34:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下微名不足挂齿
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.99,0:34:40.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你...还是跟来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.03,0:34:42.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦的家伙 除掉他
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.21,0:34:54.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难缠正是我的长处
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.34,0:34:57.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要跟我扯上关系？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.43,0:35:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对看上了的东西无道理可言
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.76,0:35:06.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这和你想救那男人的心情有什么分别？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.27,0:35:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我和那人...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.31,0:35:12.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再唠唠叨叨的 快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.65,0:35:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这场架交给我打了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.65,0:35:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必施什么礼
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.12,0:35:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死也遂愿了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.54,0:35:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要是为了喜欢的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.46,0:35:30.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是该考虑从这公司辞职了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.25,0:35:34.75,comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三一：日本古代对地位低微的武士称呼
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.25,0:35:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起来吧！你们这群三一们
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.88,0:35:37.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 有自己人来了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.36,0:35:55.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃得倒快
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.57,0:35:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把那人带哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.24,0:36:04.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是群纸老虎
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.95,0:36:08.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千代子小姐等等在下这就来
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.42,0:36:13.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那男人现在正在京都被斩首示众呢
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.00,0:36:15.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都城？
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.46,0:36:19.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚣张的小丫头的戏份到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.89,0:36:27.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那人在都城
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.73,0:36:33.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行行好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.65,0:36:36.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 绝不会放你走
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.03,0:36:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会回来
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.19,0:36:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只想见他一眼
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.95,0:36:43.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把重要的东西还到他手中
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.49,0:36:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得好听
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.66,0:36:48.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说触犯官府就要被砍头的人
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.87,0:36:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今还需要什么
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.00,0:36:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可怜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.25,0:37:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纵使你追寻几千年几千里
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.88,0:37:03.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都逃脱不了命运
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.55,0:37:07.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 还有那女人
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.23,0:37:12.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发什么呆
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.06,0:37:13.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快带走
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.48,0:37:15.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起来
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.52,0:37:18.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放手！求求你放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.44,0:37:21.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无论如何都得去
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.19,0:37:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.82,0:37:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你放开！
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.91,0:37:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,京都...比新干线快多了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.20,0:37:32.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是幕末...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.21,0:37:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寅...寅吉
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.71,0:37:40.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千代子小姐呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.05,0:37:44.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不觉得服装不对？
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.48,0:37:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.23,0:37:55.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.27,0:37:58.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘记是谁把你养大的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.94,0:38:01.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决不允许你做出给这里抹黑的事
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.19,0:38:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好记住什么叫事理
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.41,0:38:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真蠢 把咏子大姐都惹怒了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.20,0:38:10.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活该
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.70,0:38:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这千代小丫头太狂妄了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.50,0:38:16.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千代子太不把别人放在眼里了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.34,0:38:18.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.09,0:38:19.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.13,0:38:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔细看守别让她逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.59,0:38:23.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.43,0:38:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在做的是纪录片吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.68,0:38:34.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.56,0:38:35.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才叫
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.02,0:38:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“七变化 藤原千代子传说”！
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.40,0:38:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近的老头怎么都这样子
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.37,0:38:52.37,comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太夫：日本古时对高级妓女的称呼
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.37,0:38:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吗？太夫
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.08,0:38:56.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没大碍
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.87,0:38:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.92,0:39:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 快从这走
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.51,0:39:08.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那男人到这城里了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.26,0:39:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得知这消息我还能把你关在这吗
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.93,0:39:17.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大恩大德小女永生难忘
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.85,0:39:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.06,0:39:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从你来到这开始
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.57,0:39:24.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就对你有一种似曾相识的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.49,0:39:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之后就一直想为你做些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.78,0:39:33.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以...所以从那时开始！
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.91,0:39:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千代子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.33,0:39:40.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你有点职业精神
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.59,0:39:47.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说是逃狱
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.26,0:39:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冒犯官府的浪人象是逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.86,0:40:03.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,散开 别聚在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.58,0:40:14.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼！
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.70,0:40:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.58,0:40:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我 还记得我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.80,0:40:29.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那次的冬日下我也是这样偶然和你...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.72,0:40:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直...在找你
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.77,0:40:44.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想把这交还给你
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.86,0:40:46.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那！绕到那去！
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.94,0:40:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个也别放跑！
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.15,0:40:49.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.53,0:40:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.24,0:40:51.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这把钥匙...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.12,0:40:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天在约定的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.29,0:41:05.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边 快！
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.84,0:41:12.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.97,0:41:15.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才这逃来过个浪人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.06,0:41:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上哪去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.89,0:41:23.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往那去了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.98,0:41:28.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.40,0:41:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪见过你？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.28,0:41:37.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这方向 你象是有意隐藏着什么
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.95,0:41:44.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说！你一定知道逃走的男人去向
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.59,0:41:53.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姑娘 尽管放心
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.13,0:41:57.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是让人好等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.85,0:42:01.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这胆敢违抗朝廷的大胆反贼
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.60,0:42:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们自己才是些看不清时代的愚蠢走狗
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.62,0:42:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姑娘 快骑上它
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.37,0:42:26.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的就交给在下...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.17,0:43:16.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太勉强的话对身体不好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.68,0:43:19.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我这样的人还如此体贴
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.68,0:43:21.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.60,0:43:24.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这恩情小人绝不会忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.54,0:43:48.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溜出学校准备到哪去？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.37,0:43:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会是想和那个民权运动家去幽会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.01,0:43:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.91,0:43:57.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,证据确凿
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.01,0:44:04.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你家仓库里发现了那个人如假包换的遗赠品
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.51,0:44:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那人留下了些什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.06,0:44:08.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道他的事
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.35,0:44:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.69,0:44:13.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的请你到署里
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.98,0:44:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说个够吧
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.46,0:44:38.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也真是倔强啊
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.43,0:44:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一早说了不就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.97,0:44:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道的事叫我怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.56,0:44:55.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 就算知道也不会说
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.19,0:44:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背叛那个人的事我绝不做！
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.78,0:45:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个天真的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.03,0:45:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也只有现在你还有余力说这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.16,0:45:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人的感情最靠不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.96,0:45:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不一样！
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.46,0:45:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使现在我也一天比一天更爱他
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.51,0:45:23.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.93,0:45:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说咏子姐她
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.26,0:45:29.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把工作来的钱全给男人了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.06,0:45:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到最后那男人还和其他女人跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.15,0:45:39.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么没女人这么供养我
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.20,0:45:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.75,0:45:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐！我救你了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.96,0:45:57.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是？
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.96,0:45:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘记了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.09,0:46:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是拉车的源之字
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.80,0:46:04.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就象当初约定的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.72,0:46:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来此报恩了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.90,0:46:20.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的能出去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.61,0:46:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说的没错吧 小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.65,0:46:25.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没你的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.78,0:46:27.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当事人已经抓到
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.63,0:46:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.30,0:46:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.93,0:46:53.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等！ 拜托！
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.15,0:47:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开门 请开门
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.78,0:47:05.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开门 求求了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.78,0:47:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一眼...我只想看一眼
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.49,0:47:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求了 开门
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.70,0:47:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求您了 开门
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.55,0:47:29.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次又上哪去？
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.92,0:47:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是拍科幻电影吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.71,0:47:59.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜！
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.55,0:48:07.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是让人操心的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.22,0:48:11.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但房子和仓库都会被烧掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.64,0:48:14.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个傻丫头
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.31,0:48:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都这么大了还以为可以任性去死吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.10,0:48:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千代！
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.06,0:48:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千代子君！
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.77,0:48:21.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千代子！
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.57,0:48:23.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千代子君快回来
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.03,0:48:25.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回来！
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.57,0:48:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千代子君！
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.82,0:48:30.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 过来！
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.37,0:49:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.44,0:50:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(110,200)}{\fs18}总\N有\N一\N天
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.53,0:50:30.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(70,250)}总\N有\N一\N天
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.58,0:50:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千代子小姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.88,0:50:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千代子小姐 千代子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.30,0:50:52.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧 千代子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.13,0:50:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千代子小姐 千代子小姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.65,0:51:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法逃脱 无法逃脱
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.92,0:51:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您不要紧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.51,0:51:41.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里有不适吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.93,0:51:42.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.31,0:51:44.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让医生说起来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.27,0:51:47.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上了年纪谁都会变成病人
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.44,0:51:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,采访是不是改日再...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.74,0:51:55.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.61,0:51:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了明天 就再也回想不起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.87,0:52:08.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战后的混乱中
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.71,0:52:11.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家为生存而竭尽全力
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.00,0:52:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既没食物没衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.01,0:52:20.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制作好的电影是支撑大家的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.68,0:52:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是忙忙碌碌的每一天
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.44,0:52:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不论在什么时候我都...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.07,0:52:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信总有一天能够见到他
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.03,0:52:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使世上变的面目全非
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.87,0:52:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连一点线索都找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.79,0:52:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.83,0:52:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那人会看到我演的电影
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.76,0:53:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确昭和30年前后是最忙碌的时期啊
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.44,0:53:09.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露馅了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.44,0:53:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立花先生当时在银映？大泷的组里？
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.03,0:53:22.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对藤原小姐来说我只是微不足道的小人物
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.53,0:53:25.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好狡猾啊 瞒着不告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.66,0:53:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我那时...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.46,0:53:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用说导演 连主任也没能当成
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.96,0:53:35.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还总是被大泷导演批评
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.51,0:53:42.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫立花源也 请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.52,0:53:47.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好干
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.81,0:53:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咏子小姐 这是来见习的源也
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.15,0:53:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都很期待能和藤原千代子小姐合作
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.07,0:53:59.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演配角的话我最拿手
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.08,0:54:07.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 这个话题可不能提
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.25,0:54:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好记住
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.37,0:54:12.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演员和客人都一样
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.04,0:54:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要时常哄一哄才行
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.46,0:54:19.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有机会我给你做个样子
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.05,0:54:20.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.89,0:54:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我当时还真给他哄得团团转呢
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.45,0:54:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千代
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.37,0:54:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电影导演这个工作啊 和绘画很像
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.67,0:54:57.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,画家用自己喜爱的色彩在画板上做画
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.92,0:55:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也遇到了美丽无比的颜料
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.93,0:55:05.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你这个色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.90,0:55:18.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是用这样虚伪的台词把千代子小姐给...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.98,0:55:20.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次我也用用看
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.84,0:55:39.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.68,0:55:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.99,0:56:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.43,0:56:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.06,0:56:36.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是说要推辞掉嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.39,0:56:43.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你呀 也不能总被称作什么麦当娜给人这样捧着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.90,0:56:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人的幸福是要好好地拥有一个家庭...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.95,0:56:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我有...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.11,0:56:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 思想犯们不是一早就都释放了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.66,0:56:57.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连招呼都不会来打的人就算等也...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.79,0:57:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我要去见他
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.33,0:57:02.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可你连他是死是活都不知道不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.01,0:57:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人一定活着
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.01,0:57:09.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也不会一直年轻下去
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.18,0:57:13.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们约好了总有一天会相见
Dialogue: 0,0:57:13.72,0:57:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你早不是小丫头做梦的年纪了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.07,0:57:26.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.49,0:57:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千代 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.20,0:57:36.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是累人
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.87,0:57:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上了年纪的人可是要休息一下了
Dialogue: 0,0:57:40.87,0:57:42.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休息
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.56,0:57:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钥匙不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.44,0:58:06.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 我记得当时好像是...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.99,0:58:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咏子妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.07,0:58:14.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就吃午饭吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.62,0:58:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在可不是吃饭的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:58:17.24,0:58:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,源也君 现在舞台那边啊
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.70,0:58:22.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“公·主·殿·下”有麻烦了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.67,0:58:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求大家好好找
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.71,0:58:29.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能没有那个
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.55,0:58:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呆站着干什么 你也一起找 源也！
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.93,0:58:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 马上就找
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.43,0:58:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:58:42.27,0:58:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千代子小姐重要的钥匙
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.23,0:58:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是岛原咏子做的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.03,0:58:55.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实际情况不得而知
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.91,0:58:59.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但最后 钥匙还是没有找到
Dialogue: 0,0:58:59.70,0:59:01.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会找不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.08,0:59:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.17,0:59:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千代子小姐 那究竟是什么东西的钥匙？
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.34,0:59:09.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊是啊 我也想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.09,0:59:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.13,0:59:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我们嘛 老师
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.09,0:59:16.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:59:16.55,0:59:20.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是老师替一个很重要的人保管的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:59:21.10,0:59:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是指老师喜欢的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.10,0:59:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是信物
Dialogue: 0,0:59:24.10,0:59:25.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:59:25.69,0:59:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长得什么样子？
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.86,0:59:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是很帅？
Dialogue: 0,0:59:27.81,0:59:28.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像哪个男演员？
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.80,0:59:29.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么样子...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.11,0:59:33.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么样子的？
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.78,0:59:34.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么样子...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:39.99,0:59:41.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想不起来
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.62,0:59:45.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经...连相貌都想不起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:59:53.88,0:59:56.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明那么喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:59:56.97,1:00:00.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却连相貌都想不起来了
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.94,1:00:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.32,1:00:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.86,1:00:19.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这茶真香啊
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.45,1:00:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是园子里的香草
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.41,1:00:24.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对身体很好
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.04,1:00:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 让我们赶快继续吧
Dialogue: 0,1:00:31.63,1:00:33.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钥匙丢失之后不久
Dialogue: 0,1:00:35.13,1:00:37.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您就结婚了是吧
Dialogue: 0,1:00:37.55,1:00:39.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 和大泷
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.01,1:00:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丢失了钥匙 突然感觉心里象缺了块什么似的
Dialogue: 0,1:00:49.31,1:00:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也终于过了爱梦想的年纪
Dialogue: 0,1:00:55.24,1:00:58.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,20日 日本事件同日午后11点47分
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.28,1:01:02.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搭载美国Glenn中校的“友谊7号”
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.78,1:01:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在Cape Canaveral成功发射
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.38,1:01:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,1:02:04.01,1:02:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 让你知道了
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.93,1:02:09.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咏子小姐
Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.31,1:02:10.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,1:02:10.85,1:02:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼才导演编写的闹剧
Dialogue: 0,1:02:14.48,1:02:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了得到人气女演员
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.28,1:02:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扮演小偷的我也真是愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.12,1:02:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.74,1:02:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你身上我也吃过不少苦头了
Dialogue: 0,1:02:29.75,1:02:31.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,满洲的占卜先生...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.08,1:02:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真搞不懂自己为何要做那种丢脸的事
Dialogue: 0,1:02:36.25,1:02:37.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道对不起你
Dialogue: 0,1:02:38.46,1:02:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过那时候无论如何都想把你赶走
Dialogue: 0,1:02:41.93,1:02:43.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么那个人的去向...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:44.59,1:02:46.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么可能会知道
Dialogue: 0,1:02:46.93,1:02:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我那时做的被人抓到了把柄
Dialogue: 0,1:02:57.32,1:03:00.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但究竟我哪里惹了咏子小姐不高兴？
Dialogue: 0,1:03:01.28,1:03:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我羡慕你
Dialogue: 0,1:03:03.99,1:03:05.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的年轻
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.95,1:03:08.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了追一个男人
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.12,1:03:11.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你永远是这么年轻
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.29,1:03:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相比之下
Dialogue: 0,1:03:14.04,1:03:16.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我却是个扮演老人做陪衬的配角
Dialogue: 0,1:03:17.46,1:03:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在连嫉恨你的精神都没了
Dialogue: 0,1:03:20.96,1:03:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 事情已经过去了
Dialogue: 0,1:03:29.14,1:03:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问
Dialogue: 0,1:03:31.52,1:03:34.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们正在忙 过会儿再说
Dialogue: 0,1:03:34.73,1:03:40.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是...有客人来找千代子小姐
Dialogue: 0,1:03:54.96,1:03:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是藤原千代子小姐吧
Dialogue: 0,1:03:58.96,1:04:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次你打算干什么
Dialogue: 0,1:04:05.38,1:04:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,1:04:07.97,1:04:09.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我是谁吧
Dialogue: 0,1:04:10.89,1:04:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请回去！
Dialogue: 0,1:04:16.31,1:04:18.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被憎恨是意料之中的事
Dialogue: 0,1:04:19.48,1:04:24.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战前我作为权力的走狗做尽伤天害理的事
Dialogue: 0,1:04:25.53,1:04:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在为了能赎一点罪而这样四处旅行
Dialogue: 0,1:04:31.95,1:04:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是那个绘画的思想犯给你的
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.67,1:04:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说 希望能向对他有恩的你道一声谢
Dialogue: 0,1:04:45.84,1:04:47.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在对不起你
Dialogue: 0,1:05:07.11,1:05:08.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千代子
Dialogue: 0,1:05:27.51,1:05:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没能报答你的救命之恩
Dialogue: 0,1:05:30.39,1:05:31.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直难以释怀
Dialogue: 0,1:05:33.51,1:05:35.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很想马上就去见你
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.85,1:05:38.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但战争正日趋激烈
Dialogue: 0,1:05:40.94,1:05:44.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候战争结束 真正的和平到来时
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.69,1:05:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打算回到北海道的家乡完成那幅画
Dialogue: 0,1:05:58.79,1:06:02.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候 也想让你看看那片星空
Dialogue: 0,1:06:04.09,1:06:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我们约定的那个地方 等着你
Dialogue: 0,1:06:14.43,1:06:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个
Dialogue: 0,1:06:16.10,1:06:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是打开最珍贵东西的钥匙
Dialogue: 0,1:06:19.98,1:06:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最珍贵的东西？
Dialogue: 0,1:06:24.73,1:06:27.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当作明天的作业 我们约好了
Dialogue: 0,1:06:43.04,1:06:48.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,19点37分出发的“雪空138号”
Dialogue: 0,1:06:49.09,1:06:51.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就要发车了
Dialogue: 0,1:06:52.01,1:06:55.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请要乘车的乘客尽快前住12号月台
Dialogue: 0,1:07:03.56,1:07:06.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我嘛 你有喜欢的人了是吧
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.23,1:07:08.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初恋
Dialogue: 0,1:07:10.65,1:07:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天才是满月
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.45,1:07:16.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十四日的月亮还有明天
Dialogue: 0,1:07:18.03,1:07:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,称作明天的希望...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:24.92,1:07:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是马贼？
Dialogue: 0,1:07:26.17,1:07:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,1:07:31.38,1:07:33.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乘客们请注意
Dialogue: 0,1:07:33.68,1:07:39.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本车由于受前方泥石流影响临时停车
Dialogue: 0,1:07:40.39,1:07:41.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开门
Dialogue: 0,1:07:45.35,1:07:47.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下面的国道会有班车前来迎接
Dialogue: 0,1:07:47.90,1:07:50.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请各位乘客按照服务人员的指示...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:06.83,1:08:08.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可怜啊
Dialogue: 0,1:08:09.21,1:08:13.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你无法逃脱命运
Dialogue: 0,1:08:13.97,1:08:17.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注定被恋火焚身永世无法超脱
Dialogue: 0,1:08:17.97,1:08:19.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人在都城
Dialogue: 0,1:08:19.89,1:08:21.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要到殿下身边
Dialogue: 0,1:08:21.81,1:08:22.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,1:08:25.35,1:08:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我
Dialogue: 0,1:08:27.85,1:08:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天在约定的地方
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.03,1:08:37.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行行好吧
Dialogue: 0,1:08:40.66,1:08:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人一定活着
Dialogue: 0,1:08:42.83,1:08:44.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我要去见他
Dialogue: 0,1:08:44.54,1:08:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使现在我也一天比一天更爱他
Dialogue: 0,1:09:03.22,1:09:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定有事吧 夫人
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.60,1:09:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上车吧
Dialogue: 0,1:09:06.56,1:09:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社长 挺进入角色嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:09:10.73,1:09:11.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给我了
Dialogue: 0,1:09:12.19,1:09:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,区区北海道 一转眼就到了
Dialogue: 0,1:09:38.76,1:09:40.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险 千代子博士
Dialogue: 0,1:09:41.05,1:09:42.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人在等着
Dialogue: 0,1:10:15.88,1:10:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦身处那广阔而雪白的风景中
Dialogue: 0,1:10:19.42,1:10:24.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会有种置身于遥远星球上般不可思议的感觉
Dialogue: 0,1:10:47.20,1:10:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千代子博士 请回来
Dialogue: 0,1:10:50.33,1:10:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士！
Dialogue: 0,1:10:52.00,1:10:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要把这把钥匙交到那个人手里
Dialogue: 0,1:11:52.23,1:11:53.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,1:11:53.44,1:11:54.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,1:11:54.39,1:11:55.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你
Dialogue: 0,1:11:55.31,1:11:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你等等
Dialogue: 0,1:11:56.69,1:11:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你等等我！
Dialogue: 0,1:12:04.95,1:12:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:37.77,1:12:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会去 不管多远都会去见你
Dialogue: 0,1:13:16.64,1:13:18.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何都要去吗
Dialogue: 0,1:13:20.81,1:13:22.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约定好的
Dialogue: 0,1:13:24.07,1:13:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“一定会去见他”
Dialogue: 0,1:13:29.36,1:13:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去的话就再也回不来了
Dialogue: 0,1:13:34.41,1:13:35.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千代子小姐
Dialogue: 0,1:13:35.58,1:13:36.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险啦
Dialogue: 0,1:13:36.58,1:13:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千代子小姐 我...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:38.67,1:13:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:39.71,1:13:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对你...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:41.71,1:13:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,6...5...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:43.55,1:13:45.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4...3...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:45.77,1:13:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2....
Dialogue: 0,1:13:46.85,1:13:47.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:47.89,1:13:48.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,0
Dialogue: 0,1:13:53.60,1:13:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好剧烈
Dialogue: 0,1:14:08.82,1:14:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千代子小姐
Dialogue: 0,1:14:10.07,1:14:10.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险
Dialogue: 0,1:14:16.50,1:14:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千代子小姐
Dialogue: 0,1:14:17.50,1:14:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,1:14:28.05,1:14:28.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千代子小姐？
Dialogue: 0,1:14:28.80,1:14:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:14:29.84,1:14:30.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快挪走
Dialogue: 0,1:14:33.35,1:14:33.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千代子小姐
Dialogue: 0,1:14:35.10,1:14:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家赶快来帮手
Dialogue: 0,1:14:36.01,1:14:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动作快
Dialogue: 0,1:14:36.47,1:14:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千代子小姐 千代子小姐
Dialogue: 0,1:14:42.23,1:14:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了
Dialogue: 0,1:14:42.98,1:14:43.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,源也也在一起
Dialogue: 0,1:14:45.48,1:14:46.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您不要紧吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:14:56.28,1:14:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:58.45,1:15:00.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你保护了我？
Dialogue: 0,1:15:01.67,1:15:02.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,1:15:02.67,1:15:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,源也立大功了
Dialogue: 0,1:15:06.42,1:15:09.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我恨你 恨之入骨
Dialogue: 0,1:15:10.38,1:15:14.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,且爱你 如痴如醉
Dialogue: 0,1:15:17.60,1:15:18.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千代子小姐
Dialogue: 0,1:15:18.77,1:15:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千代子小姐怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,1:15:20.06,1:15:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千代子小姐
Dialogue: 0,1:15:23.27,1:15:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,源也你干了什么
Dialogue: 0,1:15:25.81,1:15:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么也没做
Dialogue: 0,1:15:41.50,1:15:42.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我
Dialogue: 0,1:15:42.91,1:15:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竞把救命恩人都忘记了
Dialogue: 0,1:15:46.04,1:15:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里
Dialogue: 0,1:15:47.46,1:15:49.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也完全变了样子
Dialogue: 0,1:15:51.17,1:15:52.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之后过了30年
Dialogue: 0,1:15:53.84,1:15:56.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一个人静静地生活过来了
Dialogue: 0,1:15:59.81,1:16:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,1:16:03.14,1:16:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您在北海道失踪后
Dialogue: 0,1:16:05.69,1:16:07.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明重返了电影界
Dialogue: 0,1:16:08.11,1:16:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经过那场摄影事故
Dialogue: 0,1:16:12.19,1:16:15.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您为什么又突然从众人眼前消失了？
Dialogue: 0,1:16:35.26,1:16:42.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以为不再会看第二次了...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:44.02,1:16:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明曾下定了决心要追随他到天涯海角
Dialogue: 0,1:16:46.69,1:16:48.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那究竟为什么？
Dialogue: 0,1:16:49.82,1:16:53.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那场事故中 我发觉了
Dialogue: 0,1:16:53.90,1:16:58.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经不再是那个人记忆中的我
Dialogue: 0,1:17:01.62,1:17:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我恨你 恨之入骨
Dialogue: 0,1:17:09.84,1:17:14.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不希望那个人看到衰老的自己
Dialogue: 0,1:17:35.32,1:17:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干代子小姐
Dialogue: 0,1:17:42.62,1:17:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次的好大
Dialogue: 0,1:17:45.04,1:17:45.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千代子小姐
Dialogue: 0,1:17:55.88,1:17:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你总是在救我呢
Dialogue: 0,1:18:02.39,1:18:04.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千代子小姐 千代子小姐！
Dialogue: 0,1:18:34.75,1:18:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后
Dialogue: 0,1:18:36.46,1:18:39.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千代子小姐还是没能见到键之君啊
Dialogue: 0,1:18:42.47,1:18:44.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个老人...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:50.81,1:18:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个画家直到最后都不肯开口
Dialogue: 0,1:18:56.48,1:18:59.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不得己对他进行了拷问
Dialogue: 0,1:19:01.07,1:19:03.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我杀了他
Dialogue: 0,1:19:06.12,1:19:07.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那千代子小姐...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:09.37,1:19:13.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在追寻着逝去之人的影子
Dialogue: 0,1:19:45.49,1:19:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,1:19:47.24,1:19:49.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪我太勉强您了
Dialogue: 0,1:19:50.89,1:19:51.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,1:19:52.41,1:19:54.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天真的很高兴
Dialogue: 0,1:19:55.67,1:19:58.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 已经该道别了
Dialogue: 0,1:19:59.09,1:20:00.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,1:20:00.17,1:20:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,医生也说一定会好起
Dialogue: 0,1:20:02.63,1:20:03.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撒谎
Dialogue: 0,1:20:04.18,1:20:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是不会撒谎呢
Dialogue: 0,1:20:09.10,1:20:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要悲伤
Dialogue: 0,1:20:11.89,1:20:18.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我又能去追寻那个人了
Dialogue: 0,1:20:21.11,1:20:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 钥匙我也拿着
Dialogue: 0,1:20:24.74,1:20:26.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了你
Dialogue: 0,1:20:27.49,1:20:31.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这把钥匙打开了我对那个人的回忆
Dialogue: 0,1:20:32.62,1:20:36.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在向你述说的过程中
Dialogue: 0,1:20:36.88,1:20:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我仿佛回到了那时的自己一样
Dialogue: 0,1:20:43.22,1:20:46.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次 一定能见到
Dialogue: 0,1:20:46.64,1:20:47.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见到那个人
Dialogue: 0,1:20:49.01,1:20:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会怎样呢
Dialogue: 0,1:20:50.93,1:20:54.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 也许不管怎样都没关系
Dialogue: 0,1:20:58.11,1:21:01.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:03.84,1:22:08.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我喜欢追寻着那个人的自己
Dialogue: 0,1:22:47.17,1:22:54.81,ed_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金黄色的月亮无数次攀上夜露弧顶
Dialogue: 0,1:22:55.01,1:23:02.81,ed_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一造访的夜牢中为你的梦想绽放
Dialogue: 0,1:23:02.98,1:23:10.74,ed_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眨眼间数千次黎明成为匆匆过客
Dialogue: 0,1:23:11.03,1:23:19.00,ed_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同去的船队载着所有与你在一起的日子
Dialogue: 0,1:23:35.14,1:23:42.69,ed_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会象那飘忽不定的云儿般出生
Dialogue: 0,1:23:42.98,1:23:50.74,ed_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千年间耳熟能详的声音回荡于每个月明的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,1:24:07.42,1:24:14.38,ed_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绽放吧 轮回的睡莲
Dialogue: 0,1:24:15.34,1:24:22.27,ed_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回响吧 千年的每一秒
Dialogue: 0,1:24:39.08,1:24:42.70,ed_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逢远的过去 遥远的今日
Dialogue: 0,1:24:43.08,1:24:46.67,ed_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的明天都从这里开始
Dialogue: 0,1:24:46.96,1:24:50.59,ed_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄金的日子只此一次
Dialogue: 0,1:24:50.96,1:24:54.80,ed_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除非你模糊的脸庞再次苏醒
Dialogue: 0,1:24:55.13,1:25:02.64,ed_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如同隐喻着同行的星辰一般
Dialogue: 0,1:25:02.81,1:25:10.82,ed_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花开遍地的野外记述着你的一切
Dialogue: 0,1:25:27.42,1:25:34.30,ed_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绽放吧 轮回的睡莲
Dialogue: 0,1:25:35.34,1:25:42.60,ed_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回响吧 千年的每一秒
Dialogue: 0,1:25:43.35,1:25:50.65,ed_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绽放吧 轮回的睡莲
Dialogue: 0,1:25:51.27,1:25:58.82,ed_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回响吧 千年的每一秒
Dialogue: 0,1:22:47.17,1:22:54.81,ed_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄金の月　草の露に幾万も昇り
Dialogue: 0,1:22:55.01,1:23:02.81,ed_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一に来る夜の牢で　打たれる君の夢に咲く
Dialogue: 0,1:23:02.98,1:23:10.74,ed_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞬く　間にも数千の 朝よ訪れよ
